data.author: Caitlin Minney
data.text: Woke up to a river outside my house. This is the Maribyrnong at a moderate flood level. Everyone on the street is safe and dry but slightly shocked at how quickly the street can flood #vicfloods https://t.co/GSmWDLpuO3
